{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/","result":{"data":{"wordpressPost":{"title":"Mengapa Sinetron &#8216;Law Procedural&#8217; Tidak Ada Di Indonesia?","content":"<p>Sinetron, atau sinema elektronik, merupakan bagian integral dari paket hiburan yang diberikan oleh sebuah televisi melalui <em>production house</em> dan <em>channel</em> yang ada di Indonesia. Tentu saja sinetron bukan merupakan produk ekslusif negara kita Indonesia, karena sinetron adalah produk global yang memiliki nama berbeda-beda di setiap negara. Jika di Amerika orang menyebutnya sebagai TV <em>series/drama/show,</em> kita menyebutnya dengan kata ‘sinetron’.</p>\n<p>Benda yang sama, dengan penyebutan yang berbeda.</p>\n<p>Sebagai produk tontonan dramatis, sinetron merupakan bentuk modern dari drama panggung di era pra televisi. Jika dulu sebuah drama dipentaskan di atas panggung (Broadway, Wayang Orang, Opera dll), maka kini semangat dan konsep yang sama dibuat untuk konsumsi yang lebih luas dan global.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51281\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51281\" data-attachment-id=\"51281\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-broadway/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-broadway.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-broadway\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Panggung teater Broadway. (Sumber: JCJoel)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-broadway-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-broadway.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51281\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-broadway.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-broadway\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-broadway.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-broadway-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51281\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Panggung teater Broadway. (Sumber: JCJoel)</p></div></p>\n<p>Tidak perlu pergi ke Broadway New York lagi untuk menikmati sebuah tontonan dramatis. Kini cukup menyalakan televisi dan pilih sendiri drama macam apa yang mau ditonton.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51282\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51282\" data-attachment-id=\"51282\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-nyalakantvjpg/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: YouTube&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51282\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-nyalakantv\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-nyalakantvjpg-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51282\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: YouTube</p></div></p>\n<p>Pernahkah kamu memperhatikan kalau sinetron di televisi Indonesia tidak pernah mengangkat tema “edukasi-hukum-plus-hiburan” sebagai produk jualan mereka?</p>\n<p>Sejak Orde Baru hingga hari ini, kita bisa lihat kalau tema sinetron televisi di Indonesia tidak pernah menyentuh bagian/tema soal hukum ataupun elemennya (polisi, tentara dll). Ingat sinetron bule “Hunter” (1984-1991)? Sepertinya hanya mereka yang pernah merasakan monopoli TVRI saja yang mungkin ingat sinetron tentang detektif jagoan Rick Hunter itu ya&#8230;</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51290\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51290\" data-attachment-id=\"51290\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-hunter/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Hunter.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-Hunter\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: YouTube&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Hunter-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Hunter.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51290\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Hunter.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-Hunter\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Hunter.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Hunter-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51290\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: YouTube</p></div></p>\n<p>Sementara di era yang sama, sinetron Indonesia baru mulai marak dengan tema-tema ‘aman tentram’ seperti drama keluarga “Losmen” atau “Jendela Rumah Kita”, yang melambungkan nama Dede Yusuf ke deretan superstar Indonesia pada masa itu.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51289\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51289\" data-attachment-id=\"51289\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-jendela-rumah/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Jendela-Rumah.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-Jendela Rumah\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: YouTube&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Jendela-Rumah-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Jendela-Rumah.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51289\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Jendela-Rumah.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-Jendela Rumah\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Jendela-Rumah.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-Jendela-Rumah-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51289\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: YouTube</p></div></p>\n<p>Ada kecenderungan kalau rumah produksi sinetron Indonesia, sejak jaman Orde Baru hingga hari, menghindari tema edukatif dengan dibalut kemasan hiburan di industri sinetron. Mengapa?</p>\n<p>Di saat Amerika Serikat ‘mengajarkan hukum’ pada warganya melalui sinetron bertema pengadilan seperti “Law and Order” (1990-2010) atau “LA Law” (1986-1994), rumah produksi sinetron Indonesia malah lebih memberikan tontonan dengan tema ‘si kaya versus si miskin’.</p>\n<p>Memang harus diakui, beberapa dari sinetron model ini ada yang bagus; sebut saja seperti “Sayekti dan Hanafi” dan “Keluarga Cemara”. Tapi keduanya ‘hanya’ memberikan sebuah pesan dan spirit perjuangan dalam menghadapi kesulitan dalam hidup. Bukan sebuah edukasi yang lebih spesifik, seperti gambaran lika liku sistem hukum pengadilan yang diberikan oleh “Law and Order” misalnya.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51288\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51288\" data-attachment-id=\"51288\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-laworder/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-laworder.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural&#8211;law&#038;order\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: TV.Com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-laworder-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-laworder.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51288\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-laworder.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-law&amp;order\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-laworder.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-laworder-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51288\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: TV.Com</p></div></p>\n<p>Seperti ada kecenderungan buat rumah produksi sinetron Indonesia untuk hanya memberi hiburan semu dan bahkan membodohi melalui sinetron-sinetron yang beredar di televisi Indonesia.</p>\n<p>Komedi (slapstick) plus ‘variety show’ yang lebih berupa aksi seru-seruan/lucu-lucuan mendominasi televisi Indonesia. Sinetron drama? Ada. Tapi lebih ke gambaran <em>‘ultra unrealistic’</em> alias terlalu menjual mimpi manis. Kisah anak-anak sekolahan? Ada. Tapi jauh dari kata “berkualitas” karena hanya berputar di sekitar <em>bully</em> dari anak kaya ke anak miskin.</p>\n<p>Bagian terburuk mungkin ‘sinetron’ eksploitasi orang miskin dengan narasi menyayat hati meminta belas kasihan lewat sebuah show televisi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51287\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51287\" data-attachment-id=\"51287\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-mikrofonph/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-MikrofonPH.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-MikrofonPH\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Setiap hari Indonesia mendapatkan asupan seperti ini dari televisi. (Sumber: Liputan6)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-MikrofonPH-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-MikrofonPH.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51287\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-MikrofonPH.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-MikrofonPH\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-MikrofonPH.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-MikrofonPH-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51287\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Setiap hari Indonesia mendapatkan asupan seperti ini dari televisi. (Sumber: Liputan6)</p></div></p>\n<p>Pernah ingat tidak sinetron Indonesia yang bertema jagoan seorang polisi cerdas seperti yang bisa dilihat di “CSI: Miami” (2002)? Atau soal dokter pengidap Messiah Complex seperti di sinetron bertema kedokteran “House, MD” (2004-2012)?</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51286\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51286\" data-attachment-id=\"51286\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-house/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-House.png\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-House\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sinetron drama medis yang BAGUS BANGET WAJIB NONTON! (Sumber: CyrilDason)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-House-300x158.png\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-House.png\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51286\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-House.png\" alt=\"LawProcedural-MIDHouse\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-House.png 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-House-300x158.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51286\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sinetron drama medis yang BAGUS BANGET WAJIB NONTON! (Sumber: CyrilDason)</p></div></p>\n<p>Sama. Saya juga tidak bisa ingat.</p>\n<p>Tak hanya sinetron soal hukum, medis atau  hal-hal edukatif publik lainnya. Tema patriotisme juga seperti dihindari oleh rumah produksi sinetron Indonesia. Tak perlu jauh ke Amerika Serikat; untuk bagian ini kita bisa lihat ke Korea Selatan saja. Ingat sinetron soal tentara Korea “Descendants of the Sun”? Tema seperti ini seperti sebuah alergi bagi produsen sinetron Indonesia.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51285\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51285\" data-attachment-id=\"51285\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-dots/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-DOTS.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-DOTS\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Descendants of the Sun. (Sumber: Soompi)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-DOTS-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-DOTS.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51285\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-DOTS.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-DOTS\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-DOTS.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-DOTS-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51285\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Descendants of the Sun. (Sumber: Soompi)</p></div></p>\n<h2>Apa yang Salah Dari Law Procedural?</h2>\n<p>Secara umum, dapat dikatakan kalau sinetron televisi Indonesia tidak menggunakan tema-tema berat seperti <em>law procedural</em> / berhubungan dengan hukum ataupun <em>‘dramatic action’</em> yang melibatkan aksi para penegak hukum seperti polisi, jaksa maupun pengacara. Bahkan dalam format komedik sekalipun; seperti misalnya sinetron tentang sebuah kantor polisi / Polres “Brooklyn Nine Nine” (2013). Di sinetron tentang kehidupan sekelompok polisi itu, situasinya adalah komedi dicampur drama dan aksi.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51284\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51284\" data-attachment-id=\"51284\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-brooklyn99/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-brooklyn99.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-brooklyn99\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: Affinity Magazine USA&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-brooklyn99-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-brooklyn99.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51284\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-brooklyn99.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-brooklyn99\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-brooklyn99.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-brooklyn99-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51284\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: Affinity Magazine USA</p></div></p>\n<p>Jadi memang sulit untuk menemukan jawaban definitif “mengapa sinetron dengan tema lebih edutainment tidak dibuat di Indonesia”.</p>\n<p>Pihak produser dan rumah produksi biasa berkelit dan membuat alasan kalau sinetron seperti itu tidak akan laku di pasaran. Karena penonton Indonesia senangnya yang lucu-lucu, yang norak, menghibur tanpa harus membuat berpikir. Jadilah mereka membuat sinetron yang memenuhi permintaan pasar tersebut.</p>\n<p>Tapi buat saya jawaban dari situasi tadi adalah karena mereka, para produser sinetron Indonesia, memang tidak punya niatan untuk membuat bangsa Indonesia mampu berpikir maju, taktis, logis dan memahami hal-hal penting dalam kehidupan sosial seperti <em>‘due process’</em> maupun sebuah prosedural lewat produk sinetron.</p>\n<h3><strong>Secara singkat: mereka tidak ingin bangsa besar ini menjadi pintar dan mampu berpikir.</strong></h3>\n<p>Harus diakui kalau televisi merupakan sarana dan medium terbaik dalam menyampaikan informasi dan hiburan ke publik selain internet. Ingat dulu di jaman Orde Baru ada stasiun televisi yang mencoba menggarap bidang edukasi + entertainment bernama “Televisi Pendidikan Indonesia / TPI”? Itu sebuah terobosan bagus yang sayang sekali tidak dilanjutkan karena berbagai alasan.</p>\n<p><div id=\"attachment_51283\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-51283\" data-attachment-id=\"51283\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/mengapa-sinetron-law-procedural-tidak-ada-di-indonesia/attachment/lawprocedural-tpi/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-TPI.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"LawProcedural-TPI\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Konsep maju televisi dari jaman Orde Baru yang kalah bersaing dengan program non edutainment. (Sumber: Agenda18)&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-TPI-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-TPI.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-51283\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-TPI.jpg\" alt=\"LawProcedural-TPI\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-TPI.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/LawProcedural-TPI-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-51283\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Konsep maju televisi dari jaman Orde Baru yang kalah bersaing dengan program non edutainment. (Sumber: Agenda18)</p></div></p>\n<p>Saya tidak tahu apakah suatu hari industri sinetron Indonesia akan mulai beranjak ke tema-tema yang lebih memberi penonton Indonesia suatu hiburan yang juga informatif tentang berbagai hal penting kehidupan sosial; seperti prosedur pengadilan, dunia medis maupun pemecahan kasus kejahatan lewat aksi petugas forensik kepolisian seperti sinetron luar negeri. Tapi saya harap saya masih hidup saat masa itu tiba.</p>\n"}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"id":"c8d44746-f330-56f1-8957-cd6087bae21c"}}}